name: Churchill Maduro
additionalNotes:
Found out about this cigar a few months ago from a friend who lives near this B&M store that rolls its own.  These are a must have cigar and I would compare them to any premium around.  With about 3 months of age on this cigar it is incredible.  http://www.rosariocigarsllc.com/

All there cigars are a combinaton of Dominican, Honduran, and Nicaraguan Tobacco.
